#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "TLS registry reference"
msgstr "TLS 注册表参考"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The TLS Registry is a Quarkus extension that centralizes TLS configuration, making it easier to manage and maintain secure connections across your application."
msgstr "TLS Registry 是一个 Quarkus 扩展，它将 TLS 配置集中管理，从而更轻松地管理和维护应用程序中的安全连接。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When defining TLS configurations in a single centralized location, you can use the TLS Registry to reference them from multiple components within the application, ensuring consistency and reducing the risk of configuration errors."
msgstr "在单一集中位置定义 TLS 配置时，您可以使用 TLS 注册表，以便应用程序内的多个组件引用这些配置，从而确保一致性并降低配置错误的风险。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The TLS Registry consolidates settings and supports multiple named configurations.\n"
"Therefore, you can tailor TLS settings for different application parts.\n"
"This flexibility is particularly useful when different components require distinct security configurations."
msgstr "TLS 注册表整合了各项设置，并支持多种命名配置。因此，您可以针对不同的应用程序部分定制 TLS 设置。当不同组件需要不同的安全配置时，这种灵活性尤为有用。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The TLS Registry extension is automatically included in your project when you use compatible extensions, such as Quarkus REST, gRPC, SmallRye GraphQL Client\n"
", or Reactive Routes\n"
"."
msgstr "当您使用兼容的扩展（例如 Quarkus REST、gRPC、SmallRye GraphQL Client 或 Reactive Routes）时，TLS Registry 扩展会自动包含在您的项目中。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "As a result, applications that use the TLS Registry can be ready to handle secure communications out of the box."
msgstr "因此，使用 TLS Registry 的应用程序开箱即用，即可处理安全通信。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"TLS Registry also provides automatic certificate reloading\n"
", integration with Let's Encrypt (ACME)\n"
", support for Kubernetes Cert-Manager,\n"
"and compatibility with various keystore formats, such as PKCS12, PEM, and JKS."
msgstr "TLS Registry 还提供证书自动重新加载功能、与 Let’s Encrypt（ACME）的集成、对 Kubernetes Cert-Manager 的支持，以及与多种密钥库格式的兼容性，例如 PKCS12、PEM 和 JKS。"

#. type: Title =
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Using the TLS registry"
msgstr "使用 TLS 注册表"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To configure a TLS connection, including key and truststores, use the `+quarkus.tls.*+` properties.\n"
"These properties are required for:"
msgstr "要配置 TLS 连接（包括密钥和信任库），请使用 `quarkus.tls.*` 属性。这些属性在以下情况下是必需的："

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Setting up the default TLS configuration, defined directly under `+quarkus.tls.*+`"
msgstr "设置默认的 TLS 配置，该配置直接定义在 `quarkus.tls.*` 之下"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Creating separate, named configurations by using `+quarkus.tls.<name>.*+`.\n"
"By specifying the `+quarkus.tls.<name>.*+` properties, you can adapt the TLS settings for a specific component."
msgstr "通过使用 `quarkus.tls.<name>.* 来` 创建独立的、带名称的配置 `。` 通过指定 `quarkus.tls.<name>.*` 属性，您可以针对特定组件调整 TLS 设置。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The default TLS configuration is not a fallback or global configuration.\n"
"Each named TLS configuration, or \"TLS bucket,\" must provide its own properties.\n"
"For instance, `quarkus.tls.reload-period` applies only to the default TLS configuration."
msgstr "默认的 TLS 配置并非备用配置或全局配置。每个命名的 TLS 配置（即“TLS 桶”）都必须提供其自身的属性。例如 `，quarkus.tls.reload-period` 仅适用于默认的 TLS 配置。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"As described in detail link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/main/adr/0004-using-the-tls-registry-for-clients.adoc#configuring-clients-with-the-tls-registry[here], Quarkus client extensions (such as REST, GRPC, and so on) ignore properties defined in default (that is, unnamed) TLS configurations.\n"
"The `quarkus.tls.trust-all` property is the only exception."
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/main/adr/0004-using-the-tls-registry-for-clients.adoc#configuring-clients-with-the-tls-registry[如本文] 所述，Quarkus 客户端扩展（例如 REST、GRPC 等）会忽略默认（即未命名的）TLS 配置中定义的属性。 `quarkus.tls.trust-all` 属性是唯一的例外。"

