"During its processing, OpenShift injects the CA certificate into the ConfigMap in the `service-ca.crt` file."
msgstr "`service.beta.openshift.io/inject-cabundle` 注解用于将 CA 证书注入 ConfigMap。请注意，ConfigMap 初始时没有数据——它是空的。在处理过程中，OpenShift 会将 CA 证书以 `service-ca.crt` 文件的形式注入 ConfigMap。"

