#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "link:https://letsencrypt.org[Let's Encrypt] is a free, automated certificate authority provided by link:https://www.abetterinternet.org/[Internet Security Research Group]."
msgstr "link:https://letsencrypt.org[Let’s Encrypt] link:https://www.abetterinternet.org/[是由互联网安全研究组（Internet Security Research Group] ）提供的一项免费、自动化的证书颁发机构服务。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Let's Encrypt uses the link:https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc8555[Automated Certificate Management Environment (ACME)] protocol to support automatic certificate issuance and renewal.\n"
"To learn more about Let's Encrypt and ACME, see link:https://letsencrypt.org/docs/[Let's Encrypt documentation]."
msgstr "Let’s Encrypt 使用 link:https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc8555[自动化证书管理环境（ACME）] 协议来支持证书的自动签发和续期。如需进一步了解 Let’s Encrypt 和 ACME，请参阅 link:https://letsencrypt.org/docs/[Let’s Encrypt 文档] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The TLS registry extension allows a CLI ACME client to issue and renew Let's Encrypt certificates.\n"
"Your application uses this TLS registry extension to resolve ACME protocol challenges."
msgstr "TLS 注册表扩展允许 CLI ACME 客户端签发和续期 Let’s Encrypt 证书。您的应用程序使用此 TLS 注册表扩展来解决 ACME 协议的验证挑战。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Follow the steps below to prepare your Quarkus application and automatically update it with new and renewed Let's Encrypt certificates."
msgstr "请按照以下步骤准备您的 Quarkus 应用程序，并使用新的或已续期的 Let’s Encrypt 证书自动更新该应用程序。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Ensure that a fully resolvable DNS domain name is available that you can use to access your application.\n"
"You can use this domain name to create a Let's Encrypt account and pass the Let's Encrypt ACME challenges to prove that you own this domain.\n"
"You can use link:https://ngrok.com/[ngrok] to start experimenting with the Quarkus Let's Encrypt ACME feature; for more information, see the <<lets-encrypt-ngrok,Testing with ngrok>> section below."
msgstr "请确保有一个可完全解析的 DNS 域名，以便您访问应用程序。 您可以使用该域名创建 Let’s Encrypt 账户，并通过 Let’s Encrypt ACME 验证来证明您对该域名拥有所有权。您可以使用 link:https://ngrok.com/[ngrok] 开始尝试 Quarkus 的 Let’s Encrypt ACME 功能；有关更多信息，请参阅下文 xref:lets-encrypt-ngrok[的“使用 ngrok 进行测试”] 部分。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Your Quarkus HTTPS application must use a _build-time_ property to enable a Let's Encrypt ACME challenge route:"
msgstr "您的 Quarkus HTTPS 应用程序必须使用一个 _构建时_ 属性来启用 Let’s Encrypt ACME 验证路由："

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The TLS registry can manage the challenge process from either the main HTTP interface or the management interface.\n"
"Using a management interface is **strongly** recommended to let Quarkus deal with the ACME challenge configuration separately from the main application's deployment and security requirements:"
msgstr "TLS 注册表既可以通过主 HTTP 接口，也可以通过管理接口来管理验证流程。 *强烈* 建议使用管理接口，以便让 Quarkus 独立于主应用程序的部署和安全要求来处理 ACME 验证配置："

#. type: Block title
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Port 80"
msgstr "80号端口"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Let's Encrypt ACME challenge requires that the application is reachable on port `80`, essentially `http://your-dns-name`.\n"
"Ensure the port `80` is accessible from the Internet.\n"
"It might require an explicit security policy depending on your hosting provider."
msgstr "Let’s Encrypt 的 ACME 验证要求应用程序可通过 `80` 端口访问，即 `http://your-dns-name` 。请确保 `80` 端口可从互联网访问。根据您的托管服务提供商的不同，这可能需要设置明确的安全策略。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We also recommend setting `quarkus.http.insecure-requests` to `redirect` to redirect all HTTP requests to HTTPS.\n"
"The ACME challenge accepts self-signed certificates and up to 10 redirections:"
msgstr "我们还建议将 ` `quarkus.http.insecure-requests` ` 设置为 `将` 所有 HTTP 请求 `重定向` 到 HTTPS。ACME 验证机制支持自签名证书，且最多允许 10 次重定向："

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The primary HTTP interface serves the challenge and is accessible from your DNS domain name."
msgstr "主HTTP接口负责处理该请求，可通过您的DNS域名访问。"

