#. type: Title ===
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Example: Using ZeroSSL"
msgstr "示例：使用 ZeroSSL"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To issue a certificate from ZeroSSL instead of Let's Encrypt:"
msgstr "从 ZeroSSL 而不是 Let's Encrypt 签发证书："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Each ACME provider may have different rate limits, account requirements, and supported features.\n"
"Consult the provider's documentation before using them in production."
msgstr "每个 ACME 提供商可能有不同的费率限制、账户要求和支持功能。在生产中使用之前，请查阅提供商的文档。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Testing with ngrok"
msgstr "使用 ngrok 进行测试"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "link:https://ngrok.com/[ngrok] provides a secure HTTPS tunnel to an application running on localhost and helps you test HTTPS-based applications."
msgstr "link:https://ngrok.com/[ngrok] 为在本地主机上运行的应用程序提供了一个安全的 HTTPS 隧道，并可帮助您测试基于 HTTPS 的应用程序。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "ngrok provides a simple way to get started with the Quarkus Let's Encrypt ACME feature."
msgstr "ngrok 提供了一种简单的方法，帮助您快速入门 Quarkus 的 Let’s Encrypt ACME 功能。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Start testing by reserving a domain in ngrok:"
msgstr "在 ngrok 中预留一个域名，开始测试："

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can reserve the domain by using link:https://github.com/quarkiverse/quarkus-ngrok[Quarkiverse ngrok] in dev mode or by reserving it directly in the ngrok dashboard.\n"
"You cannot use the ngrok domain to test the Quarkus Let's Encrypt ACME feature immediately."
msgstr "您可以通过在开发模式下使用 link:https://github.com/quarkiverse/quarkus-ngrok[Quarkiverse ngrok，] 或在 ngrok 控制台中直接预留域名来预留该域名。您无法立即使用 ngrok 域名来测试 Quarkus 的 Let’s Encrypt ACME 功能。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "ngrok uses Let's Encrypt and intercepts ACME challenges that the Quarkus application would otherwise handle."
msgstr "ngrok 使用 Let’s Encrypt，并拦截了原本应由 Quarkus 应用程序处理的 ACME 验证请求。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Therefore, remove the ngrok Let's Encrypt certificate policy from your ngrok domain:"
msgstr "因此，请从您的 ngrok 域名中移除 ngrok Let’s Encrypt 证书策略："

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`YOUR-RESERVED-DOMAIN-ID` is your reserved domain's ID, which starts from `rd_`; you can find it in the link:https://dashboard.ngrok.com/cloud-edge/domains[ngrok dashboard domains section]."
msgstr "`YOUR-RESERVED-DOMAIN-ID` 是您预留域名的 ID，以 `rd_` 开头；您可以在 link:https://dashboard.ngrok.com/cloud-edge/domains[ngrok 控制台的“域名”部分] 找到它。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Because ngrok only forwards ACME challenges over HTTP, start ngrok with the following command:"
msgstr "由于 ngrok 仅通过 HTTP 转发 ACME 挑战，请使用以下命令启动 ngrok："

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"`8080` is the localhost HTTP port your application is listening on.\n"
"Note that the application will be accessible from `http://YOUR-NGROK-DOMAIN` on port `80` but redirected to your local machine on port `8080`."
msgstr "`8080` 是您的应用程序监听的本地主机 HTTP 端口。请注意，虽然可以通过 `http://YOUR-NGROK-DOMAIN` 访问该应用程序（端口 `80` ），但请求会被重定向到您本地机器的 `8080` 端口。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Test the Quarkus Let's Encrypt ACME feature from your local machine."
msgstr "在本地机器上测试 Quarkus 的 Let’s Encrypt ACME 功能。"
